Place your wallpaper image here (e.g. wallpaper.png or wallpaper.jpg).

Then reference it in theme.nix:

    wallpaper = ./wallpaper.png;

When no wallpaper is provided (wallpaper = null), Stylix will generate
a wallpaper from the theme's color scheme, or the user can supply one
via nixpalette.stylixOverrides or by setting stylix.image directly.
